The createRecord function could benefit from checking if any of the string parameters are empty.

The shareRecord function could check if the sharee has already been added to the sharedWith array to prevent duplicates.

The approveShareRequest function could check if the sharee has already been approved to prevent duplicates.

The rejectShareRequest function could check if the sharee is in the shareRequestSent array before removing it to prevent unnecessary gas consumption.

